<section class="section">
  <p class="small muted"><a href="/about/">← Back to About</a></p>
  <h2>THE GABRIELITE FAMILY WORLDWIDE</h2>
  <div class="line"></div>
  <p class="lede">Thailand Province is part of a worldwide Congregation of the Brothers of Saint Gabriel, present in over <strong>40 countries</strong> across <strong>5 continents</strong> &mdash; in communion with the Generalate in Rome and with our sister congregations of the Montfortian family.</p>

  <h3 style="margin-top:40px">THREE PILLARS OF THE GLOBAL FAMILY</h3>
  <div class="line"></div>
  <div class="net-grid">
    <div class="net-card">
      <div class="net-icon">&#127963;</div>
      <h4>GENERALATE &mdash; ROME</h4>
      <p>The worldwide headquarters of the Congregation, led by the Superior General and General Council. All Provinces, including Thailand, live in communion with Rome.</p>
      <a href="https://www.brothersofsaintgabriel.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Generalate &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="net-card">
      <div class="net-icon">&#9968;</div>
      <h4>THE MONTFORTIAN FAMILY</h4>
      <p>Together with the Company of Mary (Montfort Missionaries) and the Daughters of Wisdom, we form the global Montfortian spiritual family &mdash; three congregations born of one charism.</p>
      <a href="https://www.montfortian.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Montfortian Family &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="net-card">
      <div class="net-icon">&#128591;</div>
      <h4>CONGREGATION &amp; RELIGIOUS LIFE</h4>
      <p>The charism, vocation, formation, and the three vows of Chastity, Poverty, and Obedience that guide our Religious life &mdash; preserved across the writings of Saint Louis-Marie de Montfort.</p>
      <a href="https://montfortian.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">montfortian.net &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="province-block">
    <h3 style="margin-top:48px">PROVINCES &amp; DISTRICTS WORLDWIDE</h3>
    <div class="line" style="margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"></div>
    <p class="small muted" style="margin:14px auto 22px; max-width:680px;">A selection of the principal Provinces and Districts where the Brothers of Saint Gabriel serve the Church and education today.</p>
    <div class="province-tags">
      <a class="prov-tag" href="http://montfortbrothers.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127470;&#127475; India (4 Provinces)</a>
      <a class="prov-tag self" href="/">&#127481;&#127469; Thailand</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127467;&#127479; France</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127464;&#127462; Canada</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127480;&#127468; Singapore / Malaysia</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127468;&#127463; United Kingdom</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127480;&#127472; South Korea</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127470;&#127465; Indonesia</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127472;&#127466; Kenya / East Africa</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127474;&#127468; Madagascar</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127464;&#127465; DR Congo</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127477;&#127469; Philippines</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127463;&#127465; Bangladesh</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127475;&#127477; Nepal</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127473;&#127472; Sri Lanka</a>
      <a class="prov-tag" href="https://www.stgabrielinst.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#127462;&#127482; Australia</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <blockquote class="callout" style="margin-top:48px">
    "From every nation under heaven." &mdash; <em>Acts 2:5</em> &mdash; The Brothers of Saint Gabriel are a Congregation of pontifical right, gathered from many peoples and sent into many lands, yet bound by one charism and one Rule of Life.
  </blockquote>

  <p class="small muted" style="margin-top:30px">
    Migrated from <a href="https://fsgthailand.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fsgthailand.org</a> &middot; this content (Religious Congregation worldwide) now lives on the Sacred site of the Thailand Province where it properly belongs.
  </p>
</section>

